<li id="cite_note-pmid17561634-40"><b><a href="#cite_ref-pmid17561634_40-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFMeolie_AL.2C_Rosen_C.2C_Kristo_D.2C_.27.27et_al.27.272005">Meolie AL, Rosen C, Kristo D, <i>et al</i> (2005). "Oral nonprescription treatment for insomnia: an evaluation of products with limited evidence". <i>Journal of clinical sleep medicine&#160;: JCSM&#160;: official publication of the American Academy of Sleep Medicine</i> <b>1</b> (2): 173–87. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17561634" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17561634">PMID 17561634</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Oral+nonprescription+treatment+for+insomnia%3A+an+evaluation+of+products+with+limited+evidence&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+clinical+sleep+medicine+%3A+JCSM+%3A+official+publication+of+the+American+Academy+of+Sleep+Medicine&amp;rft.aulast=Meolie+AL%2C+Rosen+C%2C+Kristo+D%2C+%27%27et+al%27%27&amp;rft.au=Meolie+AL%2C+Rosen+C%2C+Kristo+D%2C+%27%27et+al%27%27&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.volume=1&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=173%E2%80%9387&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/17561634&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Insomnia"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
