<li id="cite_note-pmid9703590-42"><b><a href="#cite_ref-pmid9703590_42-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFHornyak_M.2C_Voderholzer_U.2C_Hohagen_F.2C_Berger_M.2C_Riemann_D1998">Hornyak M, Voderholzer U, Hohagen F, Berger M, Riemann D (1998). "Magnesium therapy for periodic leg movements-related insomnia and restless legs syndrome: an open pilot study". <i>Sleep</i> <b>21</b> (5): 501–5. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9703590" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9703590">PMID 9703590</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Magnesium+therapy+for+periodic+leg+movements-related+insomnia+and+restless+legs+syndrome%3A+an+open+pilot+study&amp;rft.jtitle=Sleep&amp;rft.aulast=Hornyak+M%2C+Voderholzer+U%2C+Hohagen+F%2C+Berger+M%2C+Riemann+D&amp;rft.au=Hornyak+M%2C+Voderholzer+U%2C+Hohagen+F%2C+Berger+M%2C+Riemann+D&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft.volume=21&amp;rft.issue=5&amp;rft.pages=501%E2%80%935&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/9703590&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Insomnia"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
